      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 11.2 - 老子 11.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 11.2 - 老子 11.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>當其無，有車之用。埏埴以為器，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>but it is on the empty space (for the axle), that the use of the wheel depends. Clay is fashioned into vessels;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
