      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 11.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>故有之以為利，無之以為用。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Therefore, what has a (positive) existence serves for profitable adaptation, and what has not that for (actual) usefulness.</seg>
